<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Resolve Election Reminder</title>
  <style type="text/css">
    /* Reset styles for email clients */
    body, p, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, ul, ol, li {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.4;
      color: #000000;
    }
    /* Email container */
    .email-container {
      max-width: 420px;
      border: 1px solid #cccccc;
      margin: 10px auto;
    }
    /* Links */
    a {
      color: #7FB4F1;
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table class="email-container" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="420" style="border: 1px solid #cccccc; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td bgcolor="#002347" height="87" style="height: 87px;">
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                  <td width="50%" align="left" style="padding-left: 20px;">
                    <img src="https://resolve.vote/assets/logo.png" alt="Resolve Logo" width="109" height="27" style="display: block;">
                  </td>
                  <td width="50%" align="right" style="padding-right: 20px;">
                    <span style="color: #cccccc; font-size: 10px;">https://resolve.vote/</span>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <!-- Banner -->
          <tr>
            <td bgcolor="#EEEDF8" height="86" style="height: 86px; padding: 0 20px;">
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                  <td width="70%" valign="middle">
                    <h2 style="font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #000000; max-width: 236px;">Resolve it all—easy elections, trusted results</h2>
                    <p style="font-size: 8px; color: #1F2124; width: 220px;">If you have any questions or need assistance, contact our support team at info.resolvevote@gmail.com.</p>
                  </td>
                  <td width="30%" valign="middle" align="right">
                    <img src="https://resolve.vote/assets/vote.png" alt="Vote" width="50" style="display: block; margin-left: auto;">
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <!-- Main Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 20px;">
              <h2 style="padding: 10px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600;">Reminder: Your Vote is Waiting. Act Now with Resolve!</h2>
              <p style="font-size: 14px;">Hi {{voterName}},</p>
              <p style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">This is a friendly reminder that your election is still open! Don't miss the chance to make your voice heard.</p>
              
              <!-- Features -->
              <h3 style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 600;">What you Need to do:</h3>
              <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin-top: 5px;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="20" valign="top" style="padding-top: 5px;">
                    <div style="background-color: #90B5FF; border-radius: 50%; width: 13px; height: 13px; display: inline-block; text-align: center;">
                      <span style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 8px; line-height: 13px;">✓</span>
                    </div>
                  </td>
                  <td valign="top" style="padding-top: 5px;">
                    <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124; font-weight: 500;">Cast your vote: </span> <a href="{{electionLink}}" class="voting-link">{{electionLink}}</a></p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              
              <p style="padding-bottom: 8px; font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">It's quick, secure, and easy</p>
              <p style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">Hurry now! Voting closes on:</span> {{electionEndDate}} by {{electionStartTime}}. Make sure your vote counts!</p>
              <p style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 10px; color: #1F2124;">
                <span style="display: block;">Best regards,</span> The Resolve Team
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          
          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td bgcolor="#002347" style="padding: 20px; color: #ffffff;">
              <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                <tr>
                  <td width="50%">
                    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <img src="https://resolve.vote/assets/logo.png" alt="Resolve Logo" width="57" height="13" style="display: block;">
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <span style="font-size: 8px; color: #cccccc;">Secure Elections, <br> Trusted Results</span>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                  <td width="50%" align="right">
                    <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td>
                          <table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                            <tr>
                              <td width="20">
                                <div style="background-color: #808080; border-radius: 50%; width: 17px; height: 17px; text-align: center;">
                                  <img src="https://resolve.vote/assets/instagram.png" alt="Instagram" width="10" height="10" style="margin-top: 3px;">
                                </div>
                              </td>
                              <td width="20">
                                <div style="background-color: #808080; border-radius: 50%; width: 17px; height: 17px; text-align: center;">
                                  <img src="https://resolve.vote/assets/facebook.png" alt="Facebook" width="10" height="10" style="margin-top: 3px;">
                                </div>
                              </td>
                            </tr>
                          </table>
                        </td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td colspan="2" style="padding: 10px 0;">
                    <div style="height: 1px; background-color: rgba(203, 213, 225, 0.1);"></div>
                  </td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td width="50%" valign="top">
                    <p style="font-size: 10px; color: #cccccc; width: 164px; margin-top: 10px;">Start with Resolve: Create, manage, and monitor your elections effortlessly.</p>
                  </td>
                  <td width="50%" valign="top" align="right">
                    <p style="font-size: 8px; color: #cccccc; margin-top: 10px;">© Resolve Rights Reserved 2024</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
